{
  "meta": {
    "screen": "Inicio / Home",
    "route": "#/inicio",
    "registry": "Screens.inicio",
    "file": "js/app.js:332-443",
    "css": ["css/design-system.css (tokens y primitivos)", "css/app.css:393-604, 689-713 (bloques propios del Home)"],
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "updated": "2026-07-23",
    "extends": "design-system.json",
    "description": "Especificación completa de estructura, CSS, estilo, estados, datos y responsive de la pantalla de Inicio del prototipo BLU Empresas."
  },

  "principles": [
    "El Home responde a tres preguntas en orden: quién soy (empresa), cuánto vendí (adquirencia), qué tengo con el banco (productos).",
    "La posición consolidada fue reemplazada por 'Tus ventas' — para un comercio, la venta es el dato de portada.",
    "Cada sección de producto solo se renderiza si el usuario efectivamente tiene ese producto (no hay tabs vacíos).",
    "Todos los productos —tarjeta, cuenta, crédito, inversión— comparten el mismo shell `.prod-xl` y el mismo alto, dentro de un carrusel horizontal.",
    "Los importes obedecen al modo privacidad global (`State.masked`): se enmascaran con `••••••`."
  ],

  "anatomy": {
    "order": ["pageHead", "tusVentas", "tusProductos"],
    "container": {
      "selector": ".content",
      "padding": "var(--s-7) — 32px",
      "maxWidth": "calc(var(--content-max) + var(--s-7)*2) → sin límite en ≥1280px",
      "note": "Cada bloque se envuelve en `.section`, que aplica la animación de entrada `riseIn` (320ms, --ease-out)."
    },
    "loading": {
      "helper": "withSkeleton(view, sk, build)",
      "skeleton": "<div class=\"grid\" style=\"gap:20px\">UI.skeletonCard() × 2</div>",
      "delay": "650ms",
      "rule": "Nunca spinner de pantalla completa; el Home siempre entra por skeleton."
    }
  },

  "blocks": {
    "1_pageHead": {
      "selector": ".page-head.section",
      "purpose": "Identidad de la empresa activa, saludo y accesos rápidos.",
      "layout": {
        "wrapper": ".row.between.wrap",
        "gap": "12px",
        "columns": ["izquierda: nombre empresa + chip Cambiar + saludo", "derecha: 3 icon-btn + botón ClubMiles"]
      },
      "elements": {
        "h1": {
          "content": "DB.empresa.name",
          "css": { "fontSize": "var(--fs-24) / 24px", "fontWeight": 700, "letterSpacing": "-.01em", "lineHeight": "1.1 (override inline)" },
          "source": ".page-head h1"
        },
        "chipCambiarEmpresa": {
          "class": "chip",
          "content": "icon('building') + 'Cambiar' + icon('chevronDown')",
          "css": { "padding": "8px 14px", "radius": "var(--r-full)", "border": "1px solid var(--line)", "bg": "var(--surface)", "fontSize": "var(--fs-13)", "fontWeight": 500, "color": "var(--slate)" },
          "hover": "border-color var(--blu-300); color var(--ink)",
          "action": "toast({title:'Cambiar empresa', msg: empresas, type:'info'})",
          "a11y": "aria-label=\"Cambiar de empresa\""
        },
        "saludo": {
          "class": "text-muted",
          "content": "Hola, ${DB.user.first}",
          "css": { "color": "var(--muted)", "marginTop": "4px", "fontSize": "var(--fs-14)" }
        },
        "accionesRapidas": {
          "class": "icon-btn tip",
          "count": 3,
          "items": [
            { "icon": "send", "tip": "Transferir", "nav": "transferencias" },
            { "icon": "upload", "tip": "Pago masivo", "nav": "carga-archivo" },
            { "icon": "approve", "tip": "Aprobaciones", "nav": "aprobaciones", "badge": { "class": "badge badge--error", "value": 3, "css": "position:absolute; top:-3px; right:-3px; padding:1px 6px; font-size:10px" } }
          ],
          "css": { "size": "44x44px", "radius": "var(--r-full)", "bg": "transparent", "color": "var(--slate)", "iconSize": "22px" },
          "hover": "background var(--bg-2); color var(--ink)",
          "tooltip": ".tip con data-tip — aparece debajo, centrado (translateX(-50%))",
          "a11y": "aria-label obligatorio en cada uno (hover no existe en táctil)"
        },
        "clubMiles": {
          "class": "btn btn--secondary btn--sm",
          "content": "icon('gift') + '48.250 ClubMiles'",
          "nav": "recompensas",
          "css": { "minHeight": "38px", "padding": "0 var(--s-4)", "fontSize": "var(--fs-13)", "bg": "var(--surface)", "color": "#04195d", "border": "1px solid #031242" }
        }
      }
    },

    "2_tusVentas": {
      "selector": ".section.mb-6",
      "purpose": "Resumen de adquirencia. Encabeza el Home en lugar de la posición consolidada.",
      "header": {
        "layout": ".row.between.wrap.mb-4 (gap 10px)",
        "title": { "class": "h3", "text": "Tus ventas", "css": { "fontSize": "var(--fs-20)", "fontWeight": 600, "lineHeight": "var(--lh-tight)" } },
        "link": { "text": "Mira el detalle", "icon": "chevron", "nav": "caja", "css": "font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--primary); cursor:pointer; gap:6px" }
      },
      "grid": {
        "class": "sales-summary",
        "css": { "display": "grid", "gridTemplateColumns": "repeat(3, 1fr)", "gap": "16px" },
        "responsive": { "≤760px": "grid-template-columns: 1fr" }
      },
      "card": {
        "class": "sales-card",
        "element": "button (navega a #/caja)",
        "css": {
          "display": "flex",
          "flexDirection": "column",
          "gap": "6px",
          "textAlign": "center",
          "background": "var(--surface)",
          "border": "1px solid var(--line)",
          "borderRadius": "var(--r-md) / 16px",
          "padding": "22px 20px",
          "width": "100%",
          "cursor": "pointer",
          "transition": "box-shadow var(--dur-2) var(--ease), border-color var(--dur-2) var(--ease), transform var(--dur-1) var(--ease)"
        },
        "states": {
          "hover": "box-shadow var(--e-2); border-color var(--blu-200)",
          "active": "transform translateY(1px)",
          "focus-visible": "box-shadow var(--ring); outline none"
        },
        "parts": {
          ".sales-card__label": { "fontSize": "13px", "color": "var(--muted)", "fontWeight": 500 },
          ".sales-card__amt": { "fontSize": "30px", "fontWeight": 800, "color": "var(--ink)", "lineHeight": 1.1, "class": "num" },
          ".sales-card__amt .cents": { "fontSize": ".58em", "fontWeight": 700, "color": "var(--muted)", "note": "los centavos van en menor jerarquía vía bigMoney()" },
          ".sales-card__cap": { "fontSize": "12px", "color": "var(--muted)" }
        },
        "responsive": { "≤760px": "text-align: left" }
      },
      "cardDestacada": {
        "class": "sales-card sales-card--hl",
        "position": "primera (Ventas del mes)",
        "css": {
          "borderColor": "var(--blu-200)",
          "background": "linear-gradient(180deg, var(--blu-50) 0%, var(--surface) 60%)",
          "textAlign": "left"
        },
        "amount": { "color": "var(--primary-strong)" },
        "growth": {
          "class": "sales-card__grow",
          "content": "icon('arrowUp') + '+X,X%'",
          "css": { "background": "var(--success-bg)", "color": "var(--success)", "fontSize": "14px", "fontWeight": 800, "padding": "4px 10px", "borderRadius": "var(--r-full)", "iconSize": "15px" }
        }
      },
      "data": {
        "source": "DB.ventasResumen (VR)",
        "fields": {
          "VR.ventasMes": "Ventas del mes → card destacada",
          "VR.crecimiento": "% vs. mes anterior → sales-card__grow",
          "VR.pagosRecibidos": "Pagos recibidos → card 2",
          "VR.porCobrar": "Total por cobrar → card 3",
          "VR.periodo": "caption de cards 1 y 2",
          "VR.fechaCobro": "caption de card 3"
        },
        "formatter": "bigMoney(n) → `${int}<span class=\"cents\">,${dec}</span>` usando moneyParts()"
      }
    },

    "3_tusProductos": {
      "selector": ".section.mb-6",
      "purpose": "Productos que el usuario tiene con el banco, homologados y filtrables por tipo.",
      "header": { "title": { "class": "h3", "text": "Tus Productos" } },
      "shell": {
        "class": "card card--pad",
        "css": { "background": "var(--surface)", "border": "1px solid var(--line-2)", "radius": "var(--r-md)", "shadow": "var(--e-1)", "padding": "var(--s-6)" },
        "children": ["#prodTabs (tabs)", "#prodXlHost (carrusel)", "#prodXlExtra (resumen + CTAs)"]
      },
      "tabs": {
        "id": "prodTabs",
        "class": "prod-tabs prod-tabs--inline",
        "wrapper": ".scroll-x (scroll horizontal sin scrollbar visible)",
        "css": {
          "container": { "display": "inline-flex", "width": "max-content", "gap": "6px", "padding": "5px", "background": "var(--line-2)", "borderRadius": "var(--r-full)" },
          "button": { "flex": "0 0 auto", "minHeight": "38px", "padding": "8px 16px", "borderRadius": "var(--r-full)", "fontWeight": 600, "fontSize": "var(--fs-13)", "color": "var(--muted)", "whiteSpace": "nowrap", "transition": "background var(--dur-2) var(--ease), color var(--dur-2) var(--ease)" }
        },
        "states": {
          "hover": "color var(--ink)",
          "is-active": "background var(--blu-900) (#020b27); color #fff; box-shadow var(--e-1)"
        },
        "items": [
          { "key": "tarjeta", "label": "Tarjetas", "data": "DB.cards" },
          { "key": "cuenta", "label": "Cuentas", "data": "DB.accounts" },
          { "key": "credito", "label": "Créditos", "data": "DB.credits" },
          { "key": "inversion", "label": "Inversiones", "data": "DB.investments" }
        ],
        "rule": "prodTabsAll se filtra a prodTabs: solo entran las categorías con length > 0. El primer tab queda activo.",
        "a11y": "role=\"tablist\" en el contenedor, role=\"tab\" + aria-selected en cada botón (se actualiza al cambiar)."
      },
      "carousel": {
        "id": "prodXlHost",
        "class": "prod-strip",
        "css": {
          "display": "flex",
          "gap": "var(--s-4) / 16px",
          "overflowX": "auto",
          "scrollSnapType": "x mandatory",
          "padding": "6px 2px 14px",
          "scrollbar": "oculta (scrollbar-width:none + ::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none})"
        },
        "itemHeight": ".prod-strip .prod-xl { min-height: 219px } — homologa el alto de TODAS las categorías al de la tarjeta",
        "builders": {
          "tarjeta": "homeTarjetaCard(c)",
          "cuenta": "homeAcctRow(a)",
          "credito": "homeCreditRow(c)",
          "inversion": "homeInvestRow(iv)"
        }
      },
      "extra": {
        "id": "prodXlExtra",
        "class": "mt-4",
        "description": "Card de resumen monetario de la categoría activa + fila de CTAs.",
        "css": "card card--pad section",
        "byCategory": {
          "tarjeta": { "label": "Tus tarjetas con nosotros / Cupo disponible", "value": "N.cupoGlobalDisp", "caption": "de {N.cupoGlobal} de cupo total · compartido entre todas tus tarjetas" },
          "cuenta": { "label": "Tu saldo total en cuentas con nosotros", "value": "suma de DB.accounts con estado ≠ 'cancelada'" },
          "credito": { "label": "Total de tus créditos con nosotros", "value": "suma de DB.credits[].saldo", "masked": false },
          "inversion": { "label": "Total de tus inversiones", "value": "suma de DB.investments[].monto" }
        },
        "valueStyle": { "class": "kpi__value num", "fontSize": "22px", "fontWeight": 700, "letterSpacing": "-.02em", "animation": "countUp" },
        "labelStyle": { "class": "text-muted", "fontSize": "13px (12px en sublabels)" },
        "ctaRow": {
          "layout": ".row.wrap.mt-4 (gap 8px)",
          "buttons": [
            { "class": "btn btn--secondary btn--sm", "icon": "plus", "label": "por categoría (ver solicitarLabel)" },
            { "class": "btn btn--ghost btn--sm", "label": "Ver todo", "icon": "chevron" }
          ],
          "solicitarLabel": {
            "tarjeta": "Solicitar tarjeta adicional",
            "prepago": "Solicitar prepago",
            "cuenta": "Abrir cuenta",
            "credito": "Solicitar crédito",
            "inversion": "Invertir ahora"
          },
          "solicitarRoute": {
            "tarjeta": "onboarding-signature",
            "prepago": "ofertas",
            "cuenta": "onboarding-blu-plus",
            "credito": "sim-credito",
            "inversion": "ofertas"
          },
          "seeAllNav": {
            "tarjeta": "tarjetas",
            "prepago": "tarjetas",
            "cuenta": "cuentas?cat=cuenta",
            "credito": "cuentas?cat=credito",
            "inversion": "cuentas?cat=inversion"
          },
          "rule": "El botón de solicitud nunca es genérico: siempre nombra el producto de la categoría activa."
        }
      }
    }
  },

  "productCards": {
    "shell": {
      "class": "prod-xl",
      "element": "button",
      "css": {
        "flex": "0 0 clamp(230px, 68%, 280px)",
        "scrollSnapAlign": "start",
        "display": "flex",
        "flexDirection": "column",
        "textAlign": "left",
        "background": "var(--surface)",
        "border": "1px solid var(--line)",
        "borderRadius": "var(--r-lg) / 20px",
        "overflow": "hidden",
        "boxShadow": "var(--e-1)",
        "cursor": "pointer",
        "transition": "transform var(--dur-3) var(--ease-out), box-shadow var(--dur-3) var(--ease)"
      },
      "states": {
        "hover": "transform translateY(-4px); box-shadow var(--e-3)",
        "focus-visible": "outline 2px solid var(--primary); outline-offset 2px"
      },
      "parts": {
        ".prod-xl__media": "padding 14px 14px 0 — solo tarjetas (contiene el arte)",
        ".prod-xl__body": "padding 12px 14px 14px; flex 1; column",
        ".prod-xl__name": "weight 700; var(--fs-14); color var(--ink)",
        ".prod-xl__id": "11px; var(--muted); letter-spacing .06em; margin-top 2px",
        ".prod-xl__amt": "21px; weight 800; letter-spacing -.02em; margin-top 8px",
        ".prod-xl__sub": "11px; var(--muted); margin-top 3px"
      },
      "a11y": "aria-label=\"Abrir {nombre del producto}\" en cada botón"
    },

    "tarjeta": {
      "builder": "homeTarjetaCard(c)",
      "structure": ".prod-xl > .prod-xl__media (bank-card) + .prod-xl__body (Pagar hasta + badge)",
      "art": {
        "class": "bank-card",
        "css": {
          "aspectRatio": 1.62,
          "borderRadius": "var(--r-md)",
          "padding": "var(--s-5) / 20px",
          "background": "var(--grad-card)",
          "color": "#fff",
          "boxShadow": "var(--e-2)",
          "layout": "flex column, justify-content: space-between"
        },
        "decoration": {
          "::before": "círculo 220px, radial rgba(255,255,255,.22), top -70px right -50px",
          "::after": "círculo 160px, radial rgba(50,197,255,.35), bottom -60px left -30px"
        },
        "hover": "translateY(-4px) rotate(-.4deg) + var(--e-4)",
        "variants": { "bank-card--black": "grafito", "bank-card--indigo": "índigo", "bank-card--teal": "teal", "default": "--grad-card navy" },
        "content": {
          ".bank-card__brand": { "text": "blu", "css": "weight 800; var(--fs-16); letter-spacing -.02em" },
          ".bank-card__type": { "text": "{c.name} · {c.type}", "css": "10px; uppercase; letter-spacing .12em; opacity .82" },
          ".bank-card__kind": { "text": "Principal | Adicional", "css": "9px; weight 800; uppercase; letter-spacing .1em; bg rgba(255,255,255,.18); border 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.32); padding 2px 9px; radius 999px; margin-top 8px" },
          ".bank-card__chip": { "css": "34x26px; radius 6px; linear-gradient(135deg,#f5d98b,#c9a24b); inset ring rgba(255,255,255,.4)" },
          ".bank-card__number": { "text": "•••• {last4}", "css": "var(--fs-16); letter-spacing .12em; weight 500; class num" },
          ".bank-card__foot": {
            "css": "flex; justify-content space-between; align-items flex-end",
            "small": "9px; uppercase; letter-spacing .1em; opacity .7",
            "left": { "label": "Saldo consumido", "value": "money(c.deudaTotal)" },
            "right": { "label": "Total a pagar", "value": "money(c.pagoTotal) o 'Al día'", "align": "right" }
          }
        },
        "rule": "'Pagar hasta {fecha}' NUNCA va sobre el arte: se muestra en el body, debajo."
      },
      "body": {
        "layout": ".row.between (gap 8px)",
        "left": { "class": "prod-xl__sub", "text": "Pagar hasta {c.pago} (vacío si está al día)", "css": "margin:0" },
        "right": {
          "badge": {
            "pagoTotal > 0": "badge badge--warning con <span class=\"dot\"></span> + 'Por pagar'",
            "pagoTotal = 0": "badge badge--success + 'Al día'"
          }
        }
      },
      "a11y": "aria-label del arte: role=\"group\" + \"Tarjeta {name} {kind} terminación {last4}\"; tabindex=\"0\""
    },

    "cuentaCreditoInversion": {
      "builders": ["homeAcctRow(a)", "homeCreditRow(c)", "homeInvestRow(iv)"],
      "variant": "prod-xl acct-card-plain",
      "description": "Card plana, sin arte de tarjeta, contenido centrado. Homologa los tres productos.",
      "baseCss": {
        ".acct-card-plain .prod-xl__body": "align-items center; text-align center; padding 24px top / 20px bottom",
        ".acct-card-plain .prod__ic": "64x64px; radius 16px (icono 28px)",
        ".acct-card-plain .prod-xl__name": "17px; margin-top 2px",
        ".acct-card-plain .prod-xl__id": "13px; margin-top 4px",
        ".acct-card-plain .prod-xl__sub": "13px; margin-top 6px; line-height 1.4"
      },
      "carouselOverrides": {
        "context": ".prod-strip .acct-card-plain — compacta la card para igualar el alto de la tarjeta (219px)",
        "rules": {
          ".prod-xl__body": "padding 14px arriba/abajo; justify-content center",
          ".prod__ic": "42x42px; radius 12px; margin-bottom 4px !important (icono 21px)",
          ".prod-xl__name": "15px",
          ".prod-xl__id": "12px; margin-top 2px",
          ".prod-xl__amt": "margin-top 8px !important (tamaño 22px por estilo inline)",
          ".prod-xl__sub": "12px; margin-top 3px; nowrap + ellipsis",
          ".acct-interes": "margin-top 8px !important; font-size 12px; padding 4px 10px"
        }
      },
      "icon": {
        "class": "prod__ic prod__ic--{acct|credit|invest}",
        "inline": "margin: 0 auto 8px",
        "tints": {
          "acct": { "bg": "rgba(42,63,110,.12)", "fg": "#2E4A82", "icon": "wallet", "label": "navy corporativo" },
          "credit": { "bg": "rgba(84,91,108,.15)", "fg": "#4A5262", "icon": "coins", "label": "grafito" },
          "invest": { "bg": "rgba(70,63,156,.14)", "fg": "#453FA0", "icon": "chart", "label": "índigo" }
        }
      },
      "pill": {
        "class": "acct-interes",
        "purpose": "Dato destacado de la card: interés del mes o estado del crédito.",
        "css": {
          "display": "inline-flex",
          "alignSelf": "center",
          "gap": "5px",
          "marginTop": "16px",
          "background": "var(--success-bg)",
          "color": "var(--success)",
          "fontSize": "13px",
          "fontWeight": 800,
          "padding": "6px 13px",
          "borderRadius": "var(--r-full)",
          "boxShadow": "0 2px 8px rgba(11,127,69,.18)",
          "border": "1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--success) 25%, transparent)",
          "iconSize": "15px",
          "strong": "font-weight 900"
        },
        "variants": {
          "acct-interes--warn": { "bg": "var(--warn-bg)", "color": "var(--warn)", "shadow": "0 2px 8px rgba(183,121,31,.18)" },
          "acct-interes--danger": { "bg": "var(--error-bg)", "color": "var(--error)", "shadow": "0 2px 8px rgba(220,38,38,.18)" }
        }
      },
      "perProduct": {
        "cuenta": {
          "name": "a.name",
          "id": "{a.type} · {a.num} (+ ' · Cancelada' si aplica)",
          "amount": "money(a.saldo) — enmascarable",
          "sub": "'Saldo disponible' | 'Saldo por retirar · cuenta cerrada' si cancelada",
          "pill": "a.interesMes → '+{monto} este mes' (verde) | si cancelada → acct-interes--warn 'Retira tu saldo' con icono alert"
        },
        "credito": {
          "name": "c.name",
          "id": "c.num",
          "amount": "money(c.saldo) | 'Consultar' si consultarDiners",
          "sub": "'Consulta el total con Diners' | 'Pago inmediato' si mora | 'Vence {c.prox}'",
          "pill": "creditEstado(c.estado) → verde (check) / warn / danger (alert) con e.label",
          "note": "El importe del crédito NO se enmascara (no depende de State.masked)."
        },
        "inversion": {
          "name": "iv.tipo || iv.name",
          "id": "···{iv.last4} · {iv.tasa}",
          "amount": "money(iv.monto) — enmascarable",
          "sub": "'Sin plazo fijo' | 'Fecha de finalización: {iv.vence}'",
          "pill": "'+{iv.interesMes} este mes' (verde, icono arrowUp) — enmascarable a '••••'"
        }
      }
    }
  },

  "state": {
    "masked": {
      "flag": "State.masked",
      "toggle": "toggleMask() → re-render completo",
      "placeholder": { "importes": "••••••", "conSímbolo": "$ ••••••", "pill": "••••" },
      "aplica": ["bank-card__foot (ambos valores)", "saldo de cuenta", "monto de inversión", "interés de inversión", "resumen de cupo/saldo/inversiones en prodXlExtra"],
      "noAplica": ["saldo de crédito", "total de créditos", "cifras de ventas"]
    },
    "theme": {
      "flag": "State.theme",
      "toggle": "toggleTheme() — persiste en localStorage['blu-theme']",
      "impacto": "Todos los bloques usan tokens semánticos, así que el Home se adapta sin reglas propias. Única salvedad: `.prod-tabs button.is-active` usa var(--blu-900), que en dark se resuelve al valor oscuro del skin."
    },
    "tabActiva": {
      "storage": "no persiste — al re-render vuelve a prodTabs[0]",
      "handler": "onclick sobre #prodTabs [data-c] → limpia .is-active y aria-selected, activa el clickeado, llama renderProducts(kind)"
    }
  },

  "responsive": {
    "≥1280px": ".content sin max-width — el Home usa todo el ancho junto al menú",
    "1080px": ".grid-4 pasa a 2 columnas (no afecta bloques propios del Home)",
    "860px": "sidebar → bottom-nav; --topbar-h baja a 60px",
